  "prompt": "What's your definition of \"friends\"?",
  "response": "Friends can be defined as individuals with whom one shares a bond of mutual affection, trust, and support. This relationship often involves shared interests, experiences, and a sense of companionship. Friends offer emotional support, engage in activities together, and provide a sense of belonging. The nature of friendship can vary widely, ranging from casual acquaintances to deep, lifelong connections. Ultimately, friendship is characterized by reciprocity, understanding, and a willingness to be there for one another.",
